title: Regent Street Motor Show to roll into London on Oct 31Travelandtourworld.com
text:
Regent Street Motor Show to roll into London on Oct 31 Published  
Get up close to classic and futuristic vehicles, dating from pre-1905 up to the present day, as the largest free motor show in the UK, the Regent Street Motor Show takes over Regent Street in London.Regent Street will be closed to traffic from 10:30 until 16:00 on October 31 as hundreds of vehicles, showcasing 125 years of motoring history, go on display in the famous shopping street.This interactive celebration of motoring is perfect for car enthusiasts and families, as well as shoppers looking for a fun distraction.
